lead_paragraph: Kennedy Leonard and Alexis Robinson poured in 20 points each to lead undefeated No. 15 Colorado to a 76-64 win over Mississippi Valley State on Saturday night.

headline.print_headline: No. 15 Colorado Women Stay Unbeaten With 76-64 Win Over MVSU
